OL,7,FA police marksman who shot a man
OL,8,Fwrongly suspected of being a terrorist
OL,9,Fafter the 7/7 London bombings said he
OL,10,Fwas certain "we were going to die" if
OL,11,Fhe did not act.
OL,13,FJean Charles de Menezes was killed a
OL,14,Ffortnight after suicide bombers
OL,15,Fexploded devices on three Tube lines
OL,16,Fand a London bus on July 7 2005,
OL,17,Fkilling 52 people.
