OL,7,FThe firearms officer, who has remained
OL,8,Fanonymous for nearly 20 years, has
OL,9,Fspoken publicly about his actions for
OL,10,Fthe first time as part of Channel 4's
OL,11,FShoot To Kill: Terror On The Tube
OL,12,Fdocumentary.
OL,14,FHe said Mr de Menezes' demeanour
OL,15,Fhaving been identified as a suspect
OL,16,Fled him to believe the Brazilian
OL,17,Fnational was about to detonate a bomb.
OL,19,F"Reliving it in this detail is
OL,20,Fpainful," the officer said.
