OL,7,F"I want to make sure that people
OL,8,Funderstand these decisions, although
OL,9,Fthey're taken quickly, they're not
OL,10,Ftaken lightly.
OL,12,F"Because of his actions, what he did,
OL,13,Fthe information we received, it left
OL,14,Fme with no other conclusion than I had
OL,15,Fto act or we were going to die."
OL,17,FWould-be suicide bombers targeted the
OL,18,Ftransport network again on July 21,
OL,19,Fbut their devices failed to explode.
