OL,7,FThe following day Mr de Menezes, a 27-
OL,8,Fyear-old electrician, was mistaken for
OL,9,Fone of the suspects because they were
OL,10,Flinked to the same block of flats.
OL,12,FHe was shot seven times by two
OL,13,Fmarksmen at Stockwell Tube station,
OL,14,Fsouth London, after officers followed
OL,15,Fhim onto the train carriage.
OL,17,FThe firearms officer, known only as
OL,18,FC12, said the way Mr De Menezes stood
OL,19,Fup had "triggered" something in his
OL,20,Fhead.
