OL,7,F"If I don't do something now, we are
OL,8,Fall going to die."
OL,10,FOn July 23, Scotland Yard confirmed Mr
OL,11,Fde Menezes was not connected to the
OL,12,FJuly 21 attacks.
OL,14,FDame Cressida Dick, who was promoted
OL,15,Fto Metropolitan Police commissioner in
OL,16,F2017, led the operation in which Mr de
OL,17,FMenezes died.
OL,19,FA jury cleared her of any blame in his
OL,20,Fdeath at the end of the prosecution of
OL,21,Fthe Met under health and safety laws.
